Class Wkf

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.axelor.db.Model
      • com.axelor.auth.db.AuditableModel
        • com.axelor.studio.db.Wkf

  • @Entity
public class Wkf
extends com.axelor.auth.db.AuditableModel
    This class is main workflow class. Workflow is linked with model and its formview. Workflow digram will be created using bpmnEditor widget and stored in bpmn xml format.
